{
  "texts": [
    "This module is located at the most downstream position and directly interacts with the environment.",
    "It is influenced by the profile, memory, and planning modules.",
    "This section introduces the action module from four perspectives: (1) Action goal: what are the intended outcomes of the actions?",
    "(2) Action production: how are the actions generated?",
    "(3) Action space: what are the available actions?"
  ]
}